<FONT SIZE=+1><B><A NAME="about"> About Me: </A></B></FONT>

<P>

Stefan was born in <!WA8><!WA8><A HREF="http://www.rrz.uni-koeln.de/koeln/photos.html" TARGET="resource window">
Cologne </A>, <!WA9><!WA9><A HREF="http://www.chemie.fu-berlin.de/adressen/brd.html">
Germany </A> in Spring of 1973. In 1989, he completed his Mittlere Reife (10th
grade) at the Schillergymnasium in Cologne before coming to the United States
to receive a high school diploma from Bloomington High School North (Indiana)
in 1991. Stefan received his Bachelor of Science with honors and distinction
in the field of <!WA10><!WA10><A HREF="http://www.cs.indiana.edu/">computer science</A> from
<!WA11><!WA11><A HREF="http://www.indiana.edu/">Indiana University</A> in 1994. At the moment
he is working towards a PhD at the <!WA12><!WA12><A HREF="http://www.cs.washington.edu">
University of Washington </A> with an expected completion date sometime this
century.

</P>
